text: Elisa Calsi (born 6 March 1937) is an Italian gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1956 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Italian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Italy Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:People from Lodi, Lombardy
